<section class="hero-section">
  <div class="hero-grid">
    <div class="hero-image">
      <picture>
        <img src="/assets/images/hero.jpg" alt="人工芝施工事例" loading="eager" />
      </picture>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="content-inner">
        <h1 class="hero-title">家族が集まる庭を、<br>もっと好きな場所に。</h1>
        <p class="hero-lead">自社オリジナルの高品質人工芝を豊富にラインナップ<br class="pc-only">愛知・岐阜・三重・静岡で施工実績多数</p>
        <a href="/contact/" class="hero-btn">まずは相談してみる</a>
        <img src="/assets/images/hero-sns.png" alt="SNS情報" class="hero-sns-sticker" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-section { position: relative; background: #000; width: 100%; }
  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-areas: "stack";
    min-height: 500px;
  }
  .hero-image, .hero-overlay, .hero-content { grid-area: stack; }
  
  .hero-image img { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; object-fit: cover; }
  .hero-overlay {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.6) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.3) 50%, transparent 100%);
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .hero-content {
    z-index: 3;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    color: #ffffff !important; /* 絶対に白 */
  }
  .content-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; position: relative; }
  
  .hero-title {
    color: #ffffff !important;
    font-size: 4.6rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin: 0 0 1.2rem 0;
    font-family: 'Zen Maru Gothic', sans-serif;
  }
  .hero-lead {
    color: #ffffff !important;
    font-size: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
  }
  .hero-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #4CAF50;
    color: #ffffff !important;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
  }
  .hero-sns-sticker {
    position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; width: 180px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .hero-grid { min-height: 70vh; }
    .hero-image img { height: 70vh; }
    .hero-title { font-size: 1.6rem; }
    .hero-lead { font-size: 1rem; }
    .hero-sns-sticker, .pc-only { display: none; }
  }
</style>